    public class ContinuousFunctionExpression<UD extends javax.measure.Quantity<UD>,UR extends javax.measure.Quantity<UR>>
extends uk.co.strangeskies.mathematics.expression.LockingExpression<ContinuousFunction<UD,UR>>
implements ContinuousFunctionDecorator<UD,UR>
    A basic wrapper around another continuous function which reflects all changes in that function, and propagates events to listeners. The function which is wrapped can be changed via setComponent(Expression), which will notify listeners of the modification.
